It’s not so easy, let it be. Another very
great miracle I must say, I was to go to Russia,

01:09:33.270 --> 01:09:33.520
but felt sick and I had to take rest, couldn’t
go to Russia. And the Russians had prepared

01:09:33.279 --> 01:09:33.529
for the marriages, you see. So then they thought
we could have marriages in Cabella. I said,

01:09:33.290 --> 01:09:33.540
”That’s absurd, because we can have an
English marriage, but not possible to have

01:09:33.299 --> 01:09:33.549
an Indian marriage in Cabella. Will be very
difficult. But a thing happened, you see,

01:09:33.299 --> 01:09:33.549
to convince Me. I said, “The biggest problem
will be about saris for the brides.” Because

01:09:33.310 --> 01:09:33.560
nobody can select. I have to go and select,
and how will it happen? And suddenly somebody

01:09:33.319 --> 01:09:33.569
told Me, “Mother, we have some very nice
saris.”

01:09:33.319 --> 01:09:33.569
“Very nice saris? Bring them along.” I
was amazed - there were seventy-two saris,

01:09:33.330 --> 01:09:33.580
very beautiful with very good zuri work, just
for the bride, in red color. Can you imagine?

01:09:33.339 --> 01:09:33.589
I said, “This is Shri Krishna, Who has sent
the saris, as He had supplied it at the time

01:09:33.350 --> 01:09:33.600
when Draupadi asked for saris, you see. After
that I decided, “All right, what may come,

01:09:33.359 --> 01:09:33.609
we must have the weddings.” So there might
be some, some maybe, I don’t know what will

01:09:33.359 --> 01:09:33.609
be, some handicaps, doesn’t matter, but
it’s a very big venture, I think, to marry

01:09:33.369 --> 01:09:33.619
you people here with American arrangements
and in Indian style in Italy.

01:09:33.380 --> 01:09:33.630
So all of you have to be very happy about
it and join in every way, and actually it

01:09:33.389 --> 01:09:33.639
has worked out so well that I am Myself surprised.
So, this Paramchaitanya is working, but this

01:09:33.400 --> 01:09:33.650
time specially, supplying sari is the job
of Shri Krishna, you know, and He’s done

01:09:33.400 --> 01:09:33.650
His job very well. So I wish you all great
luck for enjoying these marriages. Now the

01:09:33.409 --> 01:09:33.659
time is little too much, but because of short
time we have something to do now is to announce

01:09:33.420 --> 01:09:33.670
the marriage we have thought was the best
for the people. Imagine, they said at the

01:09:33.429 --> 01:09:33.679
most seventy or eighty marriages, now they
are one hundred. Hundred and eight!

01:09:33.429 --> 01:09:33.679
Now so, people who are remarrying, we have
arranged something else for them, but who

01:09:33.440 --> 01:09:33.690
are marrying for the first time. So if you
don’t mind I’ll ask somebody to read the

01:09:33.449 --> 01:09:33.699
names of the couples now, because we have
no time, you see. It’s such a fast running

01:09:33.460 --> 01:09:33.710
train, you know.

01:09:33.460 --> 01:09:33.710
So Yogi, the great, is going to do that.
